 students trying to understand the economic aspects of environmental maintenance.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 0aEnvironmental policyzOntario. 0aEnvironmental policy. 0aPollutionxEconomic aspects. 4aDISCOUNT-B. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Environmental Economics.2bisacsh1 aEverson, C.K., eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aSims, William, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of Toronto Press eBook-Package Archive 1933-1999z978311049094740uhttps://doi.org/10.3138/978144265375740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781442653757423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9781442653757.jpg  a978-3-11-049094-7  University of Toronto Press eBook-Package Archive 1933-1999c1933d1999  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LAEC  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_ESTMALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA18STMEE  aPDA5EBK